videos.headline: Wisconsin enters the score sheet with Ingold rushing TD
videos.description: Wisconsin's Alec Ingold takes the handoff and bulldozes his way into the end zone for a 1-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: T.J. Watt shows incredible hands on pick-six
videos.description: Purdue QB David Blough's pass is snatched out of the air by Wisconsin's T.J. Watt who easily returns the interception 17 yards for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Blough finds Yancey for 75-yard TD
videos.description: Purdue QB David Blough finds a streaking DeAngelo Yancey down the sideline for a 75-yard touchdown reception.

videos.headline: Wisconsin RB Shaw bursts through line for 33-yard TD run
videos.description: Wisconsin RB Bradrick Shaw races through Purdue's defensive line and easily scores a 33-yard touchdown extending the Badgers' lead.

videos.headline: Wisconsin DB comes down with leaping, one-handed INT
videos.description: Wisconsin DB Leo Musso reaches high and picks off Purdue QB David Blough with only one hand.

videos.headline: Badgers pour it on with a 25-yard Jazz Peavy TD reception

videos.headline: Wisconsin runs all over Purdue
videos.description: No. 7 Wisconsin runs for 221 yards and four touchdowns in a 49-20 victory over Purdue.
